{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2512860, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 479860, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "恒大金融～", "timestamp": 1631693982, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2512864, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 479860, "reply_to": 2512860, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 所以是只有恒大金融爆了是吧", "timestamp": 1631694006, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2512874, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 479860, "reply_to": 2512864, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 要爆肯定全都爆了", "timestamp": 1631694124, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2512878, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 479860, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "还有恒大地产呀，主项是房地产，资金链断裂～", "timestamp": 1631694206, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2512880, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 479860, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "为啥爆了？是资金链断了还是咋了？我刚查好像许家印卸任了", "timestamp": 1631694226, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2512886, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 479860, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "恒大不是和。。有关吗", "timestamp": 1631694259, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2512887, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 479860, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "中国最激进的地产商之一。放杠杆在各种郊区海量拿地，建巨大的社区，廉价精装修高层住宅，价格不贵。本质上是地产爆了，牵连金融，当然恒大的其他产业也会缺钱出问题", "timestamp": 1631694264, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2512890, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 479860, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "woc两个亿的债务", "timestamp": 1631694287, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2512901, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 479860, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "中国地产的逻辑是，各种渠道融资（贷款，信托，高利贷）拿地，然后让建筑商垫资建设，同时预售房子。可以想象杠杆放大的程度。中间任何一环出问题，都会造成资金链危险。", "timestamp": 1631694402, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2512920, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 479860, "reply_to": 2512901, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 所以是近期铁拳砸向房地产了吗？还是由于疫情和一系列政策使得房地产降温让其资金链断了？", "timestamp": 1631694617, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2513062, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 479860, "reply_to": 2512890, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 两万亿吧？", "timestamp": 1631696316, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2513073, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 479860, "reply_to": 2512920, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 控制房地产金融风险，降杠杆，搞了很久了。很多地产商都开始收缩，但有些头铁的不这么想。现在确实很麻烦，恒大卖了无数期房，如果崩盘，大量烂尾，会引发无数群体事件，并且很多上下游公司都会破产。救不救，怎么救是个大问题。但是如果这么烂的资本家都要用纳税人的钱去救，那也真的很无语。", "timestamp": 1631696373, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2513103, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 479860, "reply_to": 2513062, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 是的，我记错了😂dz对这么大的数字失去概念了", "timestamp": 1631696579, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2513106, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 479860, "reply_to": 2513073, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 不爽的就是，资本家赚钱就是资本家商业奇才，亏了就要整个社会承担后果，这tm什么道理啊", "timestamp": 1631696643, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2513177, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 479860, "reply_to": 2513106, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 资本主义的道理。最可笑的是，公司破产了，无数人因此遭受巨大损失，资本家却可以继续住豪宅开豪车一辈子花不完的钱。我记得穷爸爸富爸爸的作者就是用公司破产来逃避债务和税务，并因此而非常得意", "timestamp": 1631697121, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2513179, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 479860, "reply_to": 2513106, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 而且高管的理财早就全额本息赎回了😏大户的钱如数奉还，小民的钱……", "timestamp": 1631697161, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2513598, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 479860, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "企业做空绷不住了", "timestamp": 1631700972, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 4, "pid": 479860, "reply": 17, "tag": null, "text": "dz对恒大的印象仅仅停留在恒大冰泉和广州恒大\n听说最近恒大爆雷\n有无dy细说啥情况", "timestamp": 1631693958, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1631700974, "url": "", "vote": {}}}